room_title: Escape room "Psycho Pschool" by Combo & Key in Portland
room_address: 10160 SW Nimbus Ave, Suite F-2 Portland, OR 97223
room_description: As a student, you must help the Teacher's Assistant get to a bomb locked away somewhere inside the room. Using backpacks, clues, and items to help you solve puzzles, you must work together to escape the blast!
